---

<section class="py-24 bg-[#020617] relative overflow-hidden" id="riesgo">
	<!-- Threat Map Background -->
	<div
		class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 -z-10"
		style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(0, 97, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);"
	>
	</div>

	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
		<!-- Section Header -->
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2
				class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 font-sans"
			>
				El Riesgo Real: Cadena de Ataque Cibernético
			</h2>
			<p
				class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium font-sans"
			>
				Un ataque no ocurre de forma aislada. Entender la cadena de
				ejecución es vital para detener el impacto irreversible.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Three Stage Cards -->
		<div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
			<!-- Stage 1: Infiltration -->
			<div
				class="relative bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:border-white/20 group"
			>
				<div
					class="absolute -top-6 -left-2 bg-red-600 text-white text-[10px] font-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-tighter shadow-lg shadow-red-900/50 font-sans"
				>
					Etapa 01: Infiltración
				</div>
				<div
					class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-900/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-red-500/50"
				>
					<svg
						class="w-10 h-10 text-red-500"
						fill="currentColor"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					>
						<path
							d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 font-sans">
					Ransomware Crítico
				</h3>
				<p
					class="text-slate-200 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium font-sans"
				>
					El malware cifra sus sistemas centrales. La consecuencia
					inmediata es el <strong class="text-white"
						>secuestro total de datos</strong
					>, exigiendo rescates millonarios que asfixian la liquidez
					operativa.
				</p>
				<div
					class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-sans"
				>
					<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse"
					></span>
					Riesgo Inminente
				</div>

				<!-- Flow Arrow (Desktop) -->
				<div
					class="hidden md:block absolute right-[-40px] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-20 text-slate-600 group-hover:text-slate-500 transition-colors"
				>
					<svg
						class="w-12 h-12"
						fill="currentColor"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					>
						<path
							d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Stage 2: Execution -->
			<div
				class="relative bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:border-white/20 group"
			>
				<div
					class="absolute -top-6 -left-2 bg-red-600 text-white text-[10px] font-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-tighter shadow-lg shadow-red-900/50 font-sans"
				>
					Etapa 02: Ejecución
				</div>
				<div
					class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-900/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-red-500/50"
				>
					<svg
						class="w-10 h-10 text-red-500"
						fill="currentColor"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					>
						<path
							d="M12 2L1 21h22L12 2zm0 3.83L19.13 19H4.87L12 5.83zM11 16h2v2h-2v-2zm0-6h2v4h-2v-4z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 font-sans">
					Parálisis Operativa
				</h3>
				<p
					class="text-slate-200 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium font-sans"
				>
					El ataque se propaga lateralmente. Se produce una <strong
						class="text-white"
						>interrupción de servicios críticos</strong
					>; su empresa deja de producir, facturar y atender,
					perdiendo confianza cada minuto.
				</p>
				<div
					class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-sans"
				>
					<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse"
					></span>
					Parálisis Total
				</div>

				<!-- Flow Arrow (Desktop) -->
				<div
					class="hidden md:block absolute right-[-40px] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-20 text-slate-600 group-hover:text-slate-500 transition-colors"
				>
					<svg
						class="w-12 h-12"
						fill="currentColor"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					>
						<path
							d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Stage 3: Consequence -->
			<div
				class="relative bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:border-white/20"
			>
				<div
					class="absolute -top-6 -left-2 bg-red-600 text-white text-[10px] font-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-tighter shadow-lg shadow-red-900/50 font-sans"
				>
					Etapa 03: Consecuencia
				</div>
				<div
					class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-900/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-red-500/50"
				>
					<svg
						class="w-10 h-10 text-red-500"
						fill="currentColor"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					>
						<path
							d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm-2 16l-4-4 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l6.59-6.59L18 9l-8 8z"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4 font-sans">
					Sanciones Legales
				</h3>
				<p
					class="text-slate-200 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium font-sans"
				>
					La filtración de datos sensibles dispara el <strong
						class="text-white">incumplimiento normativo</strong
					> (GDPR). Resulta en multas de hasta el 4% de facturación y demandas
					colectivas.
				</p>
				<div
					class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-sans"
				>
					<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse"
					></span>
					Responsabilidad Civil
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Status Footer -->
		<div class="mt-20 text-center">
			<p
				class="text-slate-500 text-xs font-mono tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-sans"
			>
				Visualización de Amenazas en Tiempo Real
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
